---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Nibble & Noble"
  description="Nibble & Noble is written by a couple critiquing food during date nights."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl flex-1 px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 sm:py-14">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold text-nn-cream sm:text-4xl">About</h1>
    <div class="nn-prose mt-8 max-w-none px-0">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-nn-cream">Nibble & Noble</strong> is our shared food diary: a couple's running critique of
        the restaurants, counters, takeout bags, and late-night cravings that end up on our date-night table.
      </p>
      <p>
        We do not always agree, which is the point. One of us may fall for the room, the other may remember the fries,
        and somewhere between those opinions is the honest version of the meal.
      </p>
      <p>
        Some nights are dressed-up tasting menus, some are eaten in the car before the food gets cold. We rate it all
        with the same appetite: honestly, enthusiastically, and as part of the story we are building together.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
